channel.title: Minecraft Songs (made for or in minecraft)
channel.description:
Basically, I have been collecting different songs that I liked (one or two is liking the song not the video). Got an opinions, ideas, etc. Lets try to make this some kind of discussion tied around songs made for (or in) minecraft.
[b]"Revenge" - A Minecraft Parody of Usher's DJ Got Us Fallin' in Love - Crafted Using Noteblocks[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPJUBQd-PNM
[b]"TNT" - A Minecraft Parody of Taio Cruz's Dynamite - Crafted Using Note Blocks[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2rDbRUDkds
[b]Dwarf Hole (Diggy Diggy Hole) Fan Song and Animation[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fR7EAdPUqvQ
[b]Mining Diamonds ("Black And Yellow" Minecraft Parody)[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zqYflKbrF5I
[b]"Mineday" - A Minecraft Parody of Rebecca Black's Friday[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TkOMpPfsVf0
[b]"Creeper Face" *Lady GaGa/MineCraft Parody* by Bobby Yarsulik[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pZCzlKCZzDk&feature=related
[b]Minecraft Song (Minecraft Everyday!) by Ceps[/b] http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWi6w8lGCpI
